      "body":"We have observed the flickering issue in other areas of the project, not just in Athena. \r\n\r\nSo far we have observed it when:\r\n- navigating the list of elements in Athena  \r\n- navigating blocks on Daily Pages with the down arrow key  \r\n- using arrow keys to navigate the dropdown menu for inline search\r\n\r\nWe think that the flickering is because of the `selected` class changing on re-render, but we have not successfully proven this yet. At this point, we are thinking the flickering issue could be a rabbit hole and will likely make a separate issue. ",
